1012
01:20:20,020 --> 01:20:24,860
Chuck!

1013
01:21:26,420 --> 01:21:27,670
Coi nào!

1014
01:22:03,040 --> 01:22:04,200
Chuck!

1015
01:22:04,790 --> 01:22:06,710
Anh ở đâu, chuck!

1016
01:22:31,360 --> 01:22:35,440
Chuck!

1017
01:23:19,950 --> 01:23:21,320
Anh là ai?

1018
01:23:23,450 --> 01:23:26,290
Tôi là Teddy Daniels.
